Title: Precomputed Fisher combined p-values and crup correlations database
Description: Precomputed Fisher combined p-values computed from the p-values of the accross cell-type CAGE-seq, DNAse-hypersensitive region dataset, DNAse-seqgene expression dataset CRUP-EP-gene expression dataset wilcoxon rank-sum tests. Additonaly, the database contains the precomputed crup scores correlations.
SourceType: BED(CAGE), BED(DNAse-hypersensitive), BED(DNAse-seq-gene), BED and TSV (CRUP-EP-gene and crup cor)
DataProvider: FANTOM5, big.databio.org and MPI for molecular genetics
